---
title: Beef & Cauliflower Pie with Turnip & Potato Mash Topping
description: It warms your heart (and stomach) when you can get your hands on a beef pie. Bake this one in a saucy veggie and beef filling. You’ll love the smokey roast cauliflower and the mash topping adds that beloved flavour - nostalgia. Enjoy!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
